  {
    "text": "up.",
    "start": 246.64,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 254.23,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "must have been damn near 12 ft tall. We",
    "start": 265.04,
    "duration": 5.719
  },
  {
    "text": "didn't hear nothing except",
    "start": 268.0,
    "duration": 6.479
  },
  {
    "text": "twigs. Then it just came upon us. Got",
    "start": 270.759,
    "duration": 7.521
  },
  {
    "text": "Riley, just gutted him. You got",
    "start": 274.479,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": "Eddie ripped through the tent, knocked",
    "start": 278.28,
    "duration": 5.639
  },
  {
    "text": "over the snowcat like it was a toy.",
    "start": 280.56,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "You're the one who's attacked by the",
    "start": 283.919,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "grizzly.",
    "start": 285.199,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm the one that",
    "start": 288.56,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "survived. I'd like to buy this man a",
    "start": 296.84,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "drink.",
    "start": 299.12,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "What's your name, mister?",
    "start": 303.36,
    "duration": 3.64
  },
  {
    "text": "It's",
    "start": 314.639,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": "Logan. And that's a poison broadhead,",
    "start": 315.88,
    "duration": 7.28
  },
  {
    "text": "which last I heard was illegal.",
    "start": 318.88,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "[Applause]",
    "start": 328.28,
    "duration": 3.21
  },
  {
    "text": "Go ahead, ask me where I found him.",
    "start": 332.88,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Ask me",
    "start": 345.039,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "where did you find it? Well, funny you",
    "start": 347.12,
    "duration": 4.799
  },
  {
    "text": "should ask. I pulled it out of the back",
    "start": 349.199,
    "duration": 3.801
  },
  {
    "text": "of a",
    "start": 351.919,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "grizzly shot and didn't have the wind or",
    "start": 353.0,
    "duration": 4.919
  },
  {
    "text": "the balls to track the animal properly",
    "start": 355.759,
    "duration": 5.121
  },
  {
    "text": "and put it out of its",
    "start": 357.919,
    "duration": 2.961
  },
  {
    "text": "misery. Instead of dropping a lethal",
    "start": 361.24,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "dose of the poison, it bled into the",
    "start": 363.84,
    "duration": 5.359
  },
  {
    "text": "bear, made him crazy, killed five",
    "start": 366.8,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "people. I don't know what you're talking",
    "start": 369.199,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "about, cuz I don't dip my arrows on",
    "start": 370.72,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "anything. In that case, you got nothing",
    "start": 373.319,
    "duration": 4.681
  },
  {
    "text": "to worry",
    "start": 375.52,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "about.",
    "start": 381.8,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Damn, that hurt.",
    "start": 389.639,
    "duration": 4.041
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry, Jean.",
    "start": 394.4,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "I wouldn't bother with",
    "start": 397.36,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "them. Most of them will die soon anyway",
    "start": 398.84,
    "duration": 5.96
  },
  {
    "text": "without your help. Three of them a week",
    "start": 401.84,
    "duration": 7.4
  },
  {
    "text": "from now in the same truck.",
    "start": 404.8,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 421.05,
    "duration": 3.3
  },
  {
    "text": "This sword is hundreds of years old and",
    "start": 425.52,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "was named Danza by the first samurai who",
    "start": 428.08,
    "duration": 6.44
  },
  {
    "text": "used it. Danza means separator in",
    "start": 430.0,
    "duration": 7.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Japanese. The ideal weapon for",
    "start": 434.52,
    "duration": 8.64
  },
  {
    "text": "separating head and limb from body.",
    "start": 437.0,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "like",
    "start": 451.759,
    "duration": 2.321
  },
  {
    "text": "so. Unpacked him",
    "start": 454.36,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
